milestones.description: Greg Chappell's 125 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for AUS), surpassing Alan Turner's 101
Greg Chappell has become the top scorer for AUS in ODIs with 646 runs, going past Ian Chappell's 542
This is the highest match aggregate (488) involving teams England & Australia in ODIs
Greg Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (16) for AUS, going past Rod Marsh
Dennis Amiss and Mike Brearley's 161-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 158 between Dennis Amiss and Barry Wood
Greg Chappell and Robinson's 148-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 136 between Ian Chappell and Stackpole
